you will have to compile your file in the command prompt before you run it, 
but then you will also have to run it as an exe file using (yourfilename.exe)

instructions on how to compile AND run the file for beginners:

compile:

1. go into your command prompt

2. go to where your project is located (for me that would be Documents and then the respective folder)

3. type g++ and then your file (dont forget the .cpp part!) (type

now you should have an application in the same place as your source code!

running the appliacation

1. follow steps one and 2 from compile

2. type in the name of your application file (don't forget the .exe!)
